  "body": "If file hardhat.config.ts is exist, remixd 0.6.8 would auto exit when remix is connected to localhost. And remix would report below error when click any file or sub folder:\r\n```text\r\nConnection to remixd terminated. Please make sure remixd is still running in the background.\r\n```\r\n\r\nHow to reproduce:\r\n```shell\r\ngit clone https://github.com/safe-global/safe-contracts.git\r\ncd safe-contracts\r\nremixd\r\n```\r\nThen open https://remix.ethereum.org/ in chrome and connect to localhost.",
